        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 8 at 5:02PM CDT until June 8 at 6:00PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 502 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 6 miles east of
Borger, moving east at 15 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Skellytown, Sanford, Borger, and Stinnett.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
